What are microservices ?

What are the features of microservices ?
    Decoupling 
    Focus on Business Capabilities
    Autonomy - Other teams are not dependent on each other
    Agility - move in and move out services

What are advantages of microservices ?
    Independent Development
    Independent deployment
    Mixed Tech Stack
    Granular Scaling

What are the best practices that are follwed in building microservices ?
    Keep separate Data Store for each microservice
    Separate build for each microservice
    Deploy in containers
    Treat servers as Stateless

What are the challenges in Microservice Architecture ?
    Configuration management


What is Spring Cloud ?
    Complexity associated with Distributed Systems
    Service Discovery
    Redundancy
    Load Balancing
    Performance
